intelligence,

00:10:25.060 --> 00:10:28.240 align:middle line:10%
becomes how sensitive
are we to the resonance

00:10:28.240 --> 00:10:31.260 align:middle line:10%
in the room, in our hearts,
in this engage between one

00:10:31.260 --> 00:10:32.060 align:middle line:10%
another.

00:10:32.060 --> 00:10:37.000 align:middle line:84%
And music is the life
blood of vibration.

00:10:37.000 --> 00:10:37.800 align:middle line:90%
It's resonance.

00:10:37.800 --> 00:10:38.040 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: The medium.

00:10:38.040 --> 00:10:39.090 align:middle line:90%
>>MALKIN: It's frequency.

00:10:39.090 --> 00:10:40.970 align:middle line:90%
It's like the unified field.

00:10:40.970 --> 00:10:42.640 align:middle line:84%
We can't hear all
the vibrations,

00:10:42.640 --> 00:10:45.270 align:middle line:84%
like the light spectrum,
but they're there.

00:10:45.270 --> 00:10:48.400 align:middle line:84%
So what if we can develop
VQ, vibrational intelligence,

00:10:48.400 --> 00:10:51.817 align:middle line:84%
in a way that uplifts our
game, makes us more empathic--

00:10:51.817 --> 00:10:53.150 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Let's talk about that.

00:10:53.150 --> 00:10:53.820 align:middle line:90%
>>MALKIN: --connects us.

00:10:53.820 --> 00:10:56.180 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Let's talk about--
and on an ambient level

