00:11:11.980 --> 00:11:14.840 align:middle line:84%
For example, if you're
in an office space

00:11:14.840 --> 00:11:16.740 align:middle line:84%
where you have to
have really clear

00:11:16.740 --> 00:11:20.594 align:middle line:84%
left brain attention,
what kind of music?

00:11:20.594 --> 00:11:22.010 align:middle line:84%
How do you go about
creating that?

00:11:22.010 --> 00:11:25.944 align:middle line:84%
Give us some ideas of some of
the notes and chords and such

00:11:25.944 --> 00:11:27.110 align:middle line:90%
