00:11:27.110 --> 00:11:30.110 align:middle line:84%
>>MALKIN: Well, you're
bringing up my newest passion.

00:11:30.110 --> 00:11:32.847 align:middle line:84%
It's not something--
when I was 17,

00:11:32.847 --> 00:11:34.180 align:middle line:90%
