Let's talk about that in
a little bit, universally

00:11:46.600 --> 00:11:47.440 align:middle line:90%
beloved tunes.

00:11:47.440 --> 00:11:48.240 align:middle line:90%
>>MALKIN: Right.

00:11:48.240 --> 00:11:49.280 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: You know, pieces.

00:11:49.280 --> 00:11:51.863 align:middle line:84%
>>MALKIN: Yeah, I can think that
