da-da-da-da-da-- yeah,

00:11:53.845 --> 00:11:56.350 align:middle line:84%
these things have
vibrational resonance, right,

00:11:56.350 --> 00:11:58.125 align:middle line:90%
to a certain kind of energy.

00:11:58.125 --> 00:12:00.250 align:middle line:84%
I'm really passionate about
this subject right now.

00:12:00.250 --> 00:12:03.570 align:middle line:84%
And it's a new passion, because
