00:12:11.927 --> 00:12:13.510 align:middle line:84%
It's actually the
name of my private--

00:12:13.510 --> 00:12:14.040 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Furniture music?

00:12:14.040 --> 00:12:15.090 align:middle line:90%
>>MALKIN: Furniture music.

00:12:15.090 --> 00:12:17.256 align:middle line:84%
And it's actually the name
of my publishing company.

00:12:17.256 --> 00:12:19.370 align:middle line:84%
And what it refers
to is, his belief

00:12:19.370 --> 00:12:21.830 align:middle line:90%
