00:12:21.830 --> 00:12:24.570 align:middle line:84%
It sets the tone of a room
and makes you feel differently

00:12:24.570 --> 00:12:26.250 align:middle line:84%
when it's in the
room, right, and when

00:12:26.250 --> 00:12:27.560 align:middle line:90%
it's strategically designed.

00:12:27.560 --> 00:12:31.890 align:middle line:84%
Well, this is way back
in-- many people consider

00:12:31.890 --> 00:12:34.450 align:middle line:84%
the godfather of the
impressionist music movement,

00:12:34.450 --> 00:12:35.710 align:middle line:90%
right, with Debussy and Ravel.

00:12:35.710 --> 00:12:36.510 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Mm-hm.

00:12:36.510 --> 00:12:38.980 align:middle line:84%
>>MALKIN: So why--
how funny that now,

00:12:38.980 --> 00:12:42.020 align:middle line:84%
