00:13:18.280 --> 00:13:20.220 align:middle line:84%
health care green
room, the health

00:13:20.220 --> 00:13:22.590 align:middle line:84%
care-- to recharge
and deal with burnout.

00:13:22.590 --> 00:13:25.060 align:middle line:84%
So he had these
zones, and he created

00:13:25.060 --> 00:13:27.750 align:middle line:84%
a hardware and a software
with his company that

00:13:27.750 --> 00:13:31.270 align:middle line:84%
addressed this nuance
of vibrational ambient

00:13:31.270 --> 00:13:34.660 align:middle line:84%
need for people to have
certain musical supports

00:13:34.660 --> 00:13:37.810 align:middle line:84%
for certain outcomes and certain
ideal ways of being, right?

00:13:37.810 --> 00:13:39.850 align:middle line:84%
And that's what Aesthetic
Audio Systems does.

00:13:39.850 --> 00:13:43.050 align:middle line:84%
And sadly, Don died
a few years ago.

00:13:43.050 --> 00:13:44.737 align:middle line:84%
